org.restlet.data

Enum Dimension

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Dimension>
      • org.restlet.data.Dimension
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Dimension>

    public enum Dimension
extends Enum<Dimension>
    Dimension on which the representations of a resource may vary. Note that when used with HTTP connectors, this class maps to the "Vary" header.
    Author:
    Jerome Louvel, Piyush Purang (ppurang@gmail.com)
    See Also:
    Response.getDimensions()
